txt.en: 'It is important to keep our forest and pathways clean and safe. Might you pitch in and rake up any fallen leaves you might find in our village? We can use the dry leaves as kindling in the hearths.'
When neighbours work together, the Rohan Eastfold Homesteads will shine bright as the beacons.
Leaves can be found scattered within the Rohan Eastfold Homesteads.\n\nYou should rake up leaves.
